PHH MortgageMortgage Solutions for BusinessesPHH Mortgage can help you grow your mortgage business in today's changing marketing. We combine expertise in Real Estate, Private Label Solutions, Relocation Services and Loan Servicing with an unrelenting focus on operational excellence, regulatory compliance and a customer-centric approach. The success of our unique business model has enabled PHH Mortgage to become one of the top ten originators and servicers of residential mortgages in the United States.1 In 2015 alone, we closed approximately $41 billion in mortgage financing and maintained an average servicing portfolio of approximately 1.1  million loans.2Our commitment to exceptional service and regulatory compliance allows our clients to focus on what they do best, so that they can succeed in today’s complex marketplace.1Inside Mortgage  Finance, Copyright 2016.2 "PHH  Corporation Announces Fourth Quarter and Full-Year 2015 Results," February  24, 2016.Looking for a mortgage?We offer a wide variety of home loan products and we’ll take the time to help you find the one that’s right for you.  An experienced mortgage consultant is ready to answer your questions and help you get started.Contact us now for a free same-day mortgage pre-approval decision call 800-210-8849.If you have questions about your existing mortgage, please call 800-449-8767.
