PHH Corp posts Q2 loss per share $0.22
Monday, 8 Aug 2016 04:15pm EDT 
PHH Corp  : Phh Corporation announces second quarter 2016 results . Q2 loss per share $0.22 . Qtrly core loss per share $0.08 . Says "taking appropriate actions to reallocate capacity to growth opportunities and reduce expenses as necessary" . Qtrly GAAP net revenues $ 196 million versus $ 237 million . Q2 earnings per share view $-0.46 -- Thomson Reuters I/B/E/S . Says "continue to see a trend by Merrill Lynch to insource a significant portion of their mortgage production volume" . Says "in past week, Merrill Lynch has advised us of their intention to insource additional volume" .PHH says Merrill Lynch's actions would result in total volume reductions representing approximately 60 pct of their total 2015 loan closing dollar volume. 
			
Full Article





Silver Point Capital reports 8.3 pct passive stake in PHH
Monday, 18 Jul 2016 06:04pm EDT 
PHH Corp : Silver Point Capital, L.P.'s stake in PHH Corp is a passive stake .Silver Point Capital, L.P. reports 8.3 pct stake in PHH Corp as of July 6, 2016 - SEC filing. 
			
Full Article





